    <h2>News</h2>
    <dl class='indent'>
      <dt>2011.02.14 Atta cephalotes</dt>
      <dd><em>Atta cephalotes</em> <a href="http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pgen.1002007">genome paper</a> released. Sequences added to <a href="http://fourmidable-sequences.unil.ch:2011">ant blast search</a> and <a href="/2011downloads">sequence download</a></dt>
      <dt>2011.02.01 Fourmidable updates</dt>
      <dd>Sleek new <a href="http://fourmidable-sequences.unil.ch:2011">BLAST interface to search ant genome sequences.</a></dd>
      <dt>2011.01.31 Ant genomes released</dt> 
      <dd><em><a href="http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.1009690108">Solenopsis invicta</a></em>, <em><a href="http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.1007901108">Pogonomyrmex barbatus</a></em> and <em><a href="http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.1008617108">Linepithema humile</a></em> genomes released online in PNAS.</dd>
    </dl>

    
